e und Briefe. Wissenschaftliche Ausgabe</title><biblScope unit="vol">Briefe I</biblScope></series></biblStruct></listBibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName><date when="1893-07-25" n="01">25. 7. 1893</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb11324">Fischer, Samuel</persName><placeName ref="#pmb168">Berlin</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11061">Bölsche, Wilhelm</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1893-07-08_01">Schnitzler an Bölsche, 8. 7. 1893</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1893-11-14_01">Schnitzler an Bölsche, [14.?] 11. 1893</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
